{"tid":2094182,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想投你 只想投你 熱血公民 我只想投你","createTime":"2020-07-04T11:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T11:34:02.000Z","uid":92376,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e85c7e5e4692a94acb5a66988c3fcae6fb8d5e2c","tid":2094182,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"當議會遺落成遺跡 用選票刻劃成回憶<br />\n想念幾個世紀 才是刻骨銘心?<br />\n若能回到教主時期 多想把你抱緊處理<br />\n你的票多療癒 讓熱血也甦醒<br />\n失去 泰的議會 像座廢墟 像失落文明<br />\n能否 一場選舉 一線生機 能不能 有再一次 當選<br />\n想投你 只想投你 熱血公民 我只想投你<br />\n經歷了 千個萬個 投票站裡 人海裡相依<br />\n用盡了 拉票心機 推你入閘 最難解選戰<br />\n會不會 妳也 和我一樣 在等待一句 我投票<br />\n<br />\n想投你 每次區選 想投你 每次立選<br />\n想當選 每個選戰 在未來 和過去 熱血公民<br />\n想follow 每則IG 不錯過 你的蹤跡<br />\n會不會 你也一樣 等待著那句 我投熱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4iRupuNet3Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4iRupuNet3Q&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=04f03bda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4iRupuNet3Q</a>"},{"pid":"f13980affd84aa526ecd9c815bee5df86ab3a5e5","tid":2094182,"uid":60855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f903e842dbaf27703d783f6c4f935475c2eba1e3","tid":2094182,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:12:57.000Z","msg":"老鼠愛大米?"},{"pid":"1519a8ad20ad29f8109f941a6e5c199c89f3627b","tid":2094182,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f903e842dbaf27703d783f6c4f935475c2eba1e3","tid":2094182,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:12:57.000Z","msg":"老鼠愛大米?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2ffdced3994a131773c818fd8b379c0a14ff9f","tid":2094182,"uid":75046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src